<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1271391-i-m-considering-using-this-title-as-a">I&#39;m considering using this title as a summer reading assignment for my Pre-AP 10th graders. I&#39;ve started reading it, but I haven&#39;t gotten far enough to know-- what content might parents object to?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1271391'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F91289.The_Hummingbird_s_Daughter">like</a></span>

