<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/112592741-w-k-birdsong"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1586017547i/112592741._UX100_CR0,38,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/112592741-w-k-birdsong">W.K. Birdsong</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I believe parents might object to the language and the graphic violence and sexual content, but the young people would be enthralled! It is extremely <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I believe parents might object to the language and the graphic violence and sexual content, but the young people would be enthralled! It is extremely earthy and realistic. It is lovely, poetic although somewhat crude. Maybe a permission slip home to gauge how many parents would object? <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
