          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780316745468" href="/book/show/897345.The_Hummingbird_s_Daughter">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/90687503-shamiram?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
